  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2130",
  "title": "[Menu] Static values",
  "body": "Right now the menu widget reacts on the result set to provide only the most meaningful facet values for the given search. However in the case of an editorial website, this can be out of the current practice of those websites where the menu is generally static.\r\n\r\nWhat about adding an option or provide a new widget that would fetch the facet values during the init and use those values to always display options that may not be returned from the search?",
